        <title>QuickRecorder</title>
        <item>
            <title>v1.2.0</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 09:08:16 +0800</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>120</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.2.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.3</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description>
              <![CDATA[
                  <style>ul{margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 5;padding-left: 18;}</style><ul>
                  <li>修复了"屏幕区域选择器"在多屏场景下超出边界的问题</li>
                  <li>修复了多屏场景下部分窗口出现在错误的屏幕上的问题</li>
                  <li>现在"屏幕区域选择器"可随鼠标自动在多个屏幕间切换</li>
                  <li>为 "窗口选择器" 和 "应用程序选择器" 添加了多屏支持</li>
                  </ul><ul>
                  <li>Fixed: Area Selector could go out of bounds when using multiple monitors</li>
                  <li>Fixed: Some window positions shifted when using multiple monitors</li>
                  <li>The "Area Selector" can auto-switch between screens following the mouse</li>
                  <li>Added multi-screen support for "Window Selector" and "App Selector"</li>
                  </ul><img src="https://github.com/lihaoyun6/QuickRecorder/raw/main/img/donate.png" width="260"/>
              ]]>
            </description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/lihaoyun6/QuickRecorder/releases/download/1.2.0/QuickRecorder_v1.2.0.dmg" length="2797825" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="EheU97WCWo6cFkmdSfdTndsPYGabB2oMsYq6tvWZPPZnu4n0PyX+s4nwc6TyjzD6DZf4cMpok1MDrDt0eZgWDg=="/>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>v1.1.8</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 01:29:16 +0800</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>118</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.8</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.3</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description>
              <![CDATA[
                  <style>ul{margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 5;padding-left: 18;}</style><ul>
                  <li>修复了"应用程序"录制模式下, 录不到摄像头画面的问题</li>
                  <li>修复某些情况下"区域录制"录制的不是所选显示器的问题</li>
                  <li>修复"视频修剪器"在 macOS 12 系统中工作不正常的问题</li>
                  <li>允许用户在录屏的同时以画中画形式展示 iPhone/iPad 画面</li>
                  </ul><ul>
                  <li>Fixed: camera overlayer could not be recorded when recording applications</li>
                  <li>Fixed: when recording screen area, the wrong monitor may be recorded</li>
                  <li>Fixed: the "Video Trimmer" not working properly in macOS 12 Monterey</li>
                  <li>Now you can show iPhone/iPad in picture-in-picture while recording a Mac</li>
                  </ul><img src="https://github.com/lihaoyun6/QuickRecorder/raw/main/img/donate.png" width="260"/>
              ]]>
            </description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/lihaoyun6/QuickRecorder/releases/download/1.1.8/QuickRecorder_v1.1.8.dmg" length="2716609" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="HSpruBCslp/Mnu+/Jb6pGhGBEwI64+co+XTLtri6OPYvpeYU6PUcf5MYtuEI8RUgogsk2KKlsk/P+Lh3ZKgPCg=="/>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>v1.1.7</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 01:37:01 +0800</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>117</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.7</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.3</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <style>ul{margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 5;padding-left: 18;}</style><ul>
                <li>当菜单栏中的录制指示器因空间不足被隐藏时, 会自动转变为浮动窗口</li>
                <li>修复了在非 Retina 显示器上 UI 抖动和 macOS 12 上显示错位的问题</li>
                <li>修复了 "屏幕区域录制" 模式下, 无法隐藏自身窗口的问题</li>
                <li>修复了一些界面文本中的错字漏字</li>
                </ul><ul>
                <li>If the menubar item cannot be displayed, it will become a floating window</li>
                <li>Fixed UI jitter on non-Retina displays and UI misalignment on macOS 12</li>
                <li>Fixed "Exclude QuickRecorder itself" not working in "Screen Area" mode</li>
                <li>Fixed some typos and omissions in some UI string</li>
                </ul><img src="https://github.com/lihaoyun6/QuickRecorder/raw/main/img/donate.png" width="300"/>
            ]]>
            </description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/lihaoyun6/QuickRecorder/releases/download/1.1.7/QuickRecorder_v1.1.7.dmg" length="2694167" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="5fhoWd9twf/mN/DHNdZoedLXviHFU9Tl+d6CyJSj1bzmFi/w0ax9Jt0C4GLO8782YlDT49sBsxd5osacS/xPBQ=="/>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>v1.1.6</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 22:39:15 +0800</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>116</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.6</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.3</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <style>ul{margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 5;padding-left: 18;}</style><ul>
                <li>移除了不适合普通用户使用的 "像素格式" 选项</li>
                <li>新增了透明度捕捉, 可在输出中包含 Alpha 通道</li>
                <li>为 "屏幕区域录制" 添加了快捷键选项</li>
                </ul><ul>
                <li>Removed "Pixel Format" option not suitable for general users</li>
                <li>Added Alpha support to include Alpha channel in output video</li>
                <li>Added hotkey option for "Record Screen Area"</li>
                </ul><img src="https://github.com/lihaoyun6/QuickRecorder/raw/main/img/donate.png" width="300"/>
            ]]>
            </description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/lihaoyun6/QuickRecorder/releases/download/1.1.6/QuickRecorder_v1.1.6.dmg" length="2683926" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="c2869HlLfk7gm05sEMQ9weNRDwla2EfGKit5zTxUxXJQ/Xzm4WWPO97Crz+Qbv3jO2hp0u+PsLAGAl67uHieAg=="/>
